---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/main-layout.astro'
---

<MainLayout>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-primary"
        >
          About ilamy Calendar
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
          A passion project for the developer community
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Mission Section -->
        <section>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linear-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">🎯</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">My Mission</h2>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 dark:from-blue-950/20 dark:to-purple-950/20 rounded-lg p-6 border"
          >
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
              ilamy Calendar was created with a simple mission: to provide
              developers with a powerful, flexible, and beautiful calendar
              component for React applications. I believe that calendars should
              be easy to implement, highly customizable, and perform well even
              with thousands of events.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              My goal is to continue improving and expanding the calendar
              component to meet the evolving needs of modern web applications
              while maintaining a clean and intuitive API.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- About Me Section -->
        <section>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linear-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">👨‍💻</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">About Ilamy Dev</h2>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
              I'm a passionate developer dedicated to creating high-quality,
              open-source tools and libraries for the developer community. With
              a background in front-end development, UX design, and performance
              optimization, I bring experience and attention to detail to every
              project I build.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              ilamy Calendar is my passion project - a way to give back to the
              developer community and solve real problems I've encountered in my
              own projects.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Values Section -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">My Values</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div
              class="bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-800/70 rounded-lg p-6 border hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
            >
              <h3
                class="font-semibold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"
              >
                <span>✨</span> Quality
              </h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                I believe in writing clean, maintainable code and designing
                intuitive user interfaces that stand the test of time.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-800/70 rounded-lg p-6 border hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
            >
              <h3
                class="font-semibold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"
              >
                <span>🔓</span> Openness
              </h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                I'm committed to open source, transparency in my development
                process, and feedback-driven improvement.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-800/70 rounded-lg p-6 border hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
            >
              <h3
                class="font-semibold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"
              >
                <span>🚀</span> Innovation
              </h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                I continuously explore new technologies and approaches to create
                forward-thinking solutions.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="bg-white/70 dark:bg-gray-800/70 rounded-lg p-6 border hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
            >
              <h3
                class="font-semibold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"
              >
                <span>🤝</span> Community
              </h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                I value and support the developer community through
                contributions, education, and collaboration.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Story Section -->
        <section>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-linear-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">📖</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">The Story</h2>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
              ilamy Calendar is a project that was started with a mission
              to provide better calendar components for the React
              ecosystem. After recognizing the need for a comprehensive
              solution, the project was developed to address the limitations
              of existing options.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              This is still an early-stage passion project that I'm actively
              developing and refining. My goal is to eventually share it with
              the developer community once it reaches a stable, production-ready
              state.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact CTA -->
        <section>
          <div
            class="bg-linear-to-r from-purple-50 to-blue-50 dark:from-purple-950/20 dark:to-blue-950/20 rounded-lg p-8 border text-center"
          >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Want to Connect?</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
              I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers and
              hearing about your projects. Feel free to reach out if you have
              questions or just want to chat about web development!
            </p>
            <a
              href="/support"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors"
            >
              Get in Touch
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
